          "date": "2025-09-04 23:39:45.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-0000 tests: llapi EC partial, mirror-id, parity stripe size",
        "message": "LU-0000 tests: llapi EC partial, mirror-id, parity stripe size\n\n- T41: allow EC parity on partial data extent (not to EOF) and\n  validate with llapi_layout_sanity()\n- T45- T47: assert parity stays on its mirror using mirror_id\n  and flags (parity vs data)\n- T35: set/get stripe size on parity components and assert 1MiB\n\nTest-Parameters: forjanitoronly\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I0719d9cc258149ef2d6b482bd9bfa88187bfcae6\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
